data.text:
published on 2018-02-17T00:45:04Z

The Armed Forces Radio Service broadcast Command Performance during WW II and after via shortwave. Shows were not heard on commercial broadcast stations. Featured popular stars performing request songs sent in by our military overseas. This episode from February 1, 1944 features an outstanding guest cast including Dinah Shore, Bing Crosby and Frank Sinatra

Genre

Old Time Radio
